tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE DiversityInclusivityAI (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_name VARCHAR(255),
    dataset_description TEXT,
    creator VARCHAR(100),
    date_created DATE,
    inclusivity_score DECIMAL(5,2),
    diversity_score DECIMAL(5,2)
);

CREATE TABLE diversity_inclusivity_ai_training_datasets (
  id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  publication_date DATE,
  diversity_score FLOAT,
  inclusivity_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE dataset_users (
  user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_id UUID,
  user_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  user_email VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE,
  user_role ENUM('admin', 'researcher', 'contributor')
);

CREATE TABLE ai_training_datasets (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_name TEXT NOT NULL,
  dataset_description TEXT,
  diversity_score FLOAT,
  inclusivity_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE dataset_annotations (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_id INT,
  annotation_text TEXT,
  annotation_author TEXT,
  annotation_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES ai_training_datasets(id)
)

CREATE TABLE dataset_contributors (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_id INT,
  contributor_name TEXT,
  contributor_email TEXT,
  contribution_date DATE,
  FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES ai_training_datasets(id)
)

CREATE TABLE ai_training_datasets (
    dataset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    dataset_name VARCHAR(255),
    dataset_description TEXT,
    diversity_score FLOAT,
    inclusivity_score FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE dataset_users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_name VARCHAR(50),
    role VARCHAR(50),
    dataset_id INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES ai_training_datasets(dataset_id)
);

CREATE TABLE dataset (
  dataset_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  dataset_description TEXT,
  dataset_size INT,
  creation_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE data_contributor (
  contributor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  contributor_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  contributor_email VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE,
  organization VARCHAR(255),
  join_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE data_annotation (
  annotation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_id INT,
  contributor_id INT,
  annotation_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  annotation_details TEXT,
  PRIMARY KEY (annotation_id, dataset_id, contributor_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES dataset(dataset_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (contributor_id) REFERENCES data_contributor(contributor_id)
);

CREATE TABLE data_quality (
  quality_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_id INT,
  contributor_id INT,
  quality_score INT,
  quality_comments TEXT,
  PRIMARY KEY (quality_id, dataset_id, contributor_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES dataset(dataset_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (contributor_id) REFERENCES data_contributor(contributor_id)
);

CREATE TABLE data_access (
  access_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  dataset_id INT,
  access_date DATE,
  user_id INT,
  access_type VARCHAR(50),
  FOREIGN KEY (dataset_id) REFERENCES dataset(dataset_id)
);
